sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Mgr as PPC Manager
    participant AI as AI Agent
    participant Site as Business Website

    Mgr->>AI: Write ad copy for this business
    AI->>Site: Scrape the site FIRST —<br/>before writing a word
    Site-->>AI: Actual pages — services,<br/>credentials, hours, history

    AI->>AI: Extract claims — each cites<br/>its page and exact wording
    Note over AI,Site: A claim without a source does not ship.<br/>Empty beats inaccurate.

    AI-->>Mgr: Proposed copy — every line cited,<br/>unverifiable ideas listed as EXCLUDED
    Mgr->>AI: Review with sources visible —<br/>approve or trim

    opt Website unreachable
        AI-->>Mgr: State the limitation — no guessing.<br/>The human provides facts,<br/>or fields stay empty.
    end
